textObjects.text: Scorpio returns and successfully traps Nick Fury, who was scheduled to attend the unveiling of a new and improved LMD. With Fury his captive, Scorpio uses a machine to make a perfect casting of his face which he then wears as a mask to impersonate him and attend the unveiling in his place.
As an agent of S.H.I.E.L.D. Nick Fury has always been getting himself into unbelievable situations, but this cover by Jim Steranko really takes the cake!
